<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>शुभ Journey</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %>
    <div class="main-wrapper">
      <img src="images/char-dham.jpg" class="image" />
      <img src="images/RamMandir1.jpg" class="image" />
      <img src="images/premmandir.jpg" class="image" />
      <img src="images/Paragliding.jpg" class="image" />
      <img src="images/Amritsar.jpg" class="image" />
      <img src="images/NahangarhFort.jpg" class="image" />
    </div>

    <div class="experience">
      <div class="left-part">
        <div class="left-left">
          <h1>10+</h1>
          <pre>Years of experience</pre>
        </div>
        <p>
          Our 10+ years of experience in the travel and tourism industry is the
          cornerstone of our success. It's what enables us to navigate the
          intricate details and seamlessly tackle unexpected challenges. By
          combining our wealth of knowledge with cutting-edge technology, we
          have established ourselves as a formidable Travel Management Company.
          With a track record spanning over a decade, we possess the expertise
          to execute contracts with precision and the accountability to
          consistently deliver exceptional service tailored to our clients'
          needs.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- <div class="right-part"></div> -->
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="features">
        <h1>What we Offer</h1>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
            <div class="card">
              <img
                src="icons/worldwide.png"
                height="32%"
                width="32%"
                style="margin: 4vw 0 3vw 6vw"
              />
              <h5>Interactive maps</h5>
              <p>
                An interactive map allows users to explore locations,
                attractions, and routes with dynamic features like zooming,
                panning, and clickable markers for enhanced navigation and
                exploration.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
            <div class="card">
              <img
                src="icons/flight.png"
                alt=""
                height="32%"
                width="32%"
                style="margin: 4vw 0 3vw 6vw"
              />
              <h5>Travel Deals and Discounts</h5>
              <p>
                Special offers, deals, and discounts on flights, hotels,
                vacation packages, tours, and activities to help users save
                money on their travels.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
            <div class="card">
              <img
                src="icons/travel.png"
                height="32%"
                width="32%"
                style="margin: 4vw 0 3vw 6vw"
              />
              <h5>Travel Blog</h5>
              <p>
                Engaging and informative blog content featuring travel tips,
                destination highlights, insider guides, and personal travel
                experiences.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row" style="margin-top: 3vw">
          <div class="col col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
            <div class="card">
              <img
                src="icons/guidebook.png"
                alt=""
                height="32%"
                width="32%"
                style="margin: 4vw 0 3vw 6vw"
              />
              <h5>Destination Guides</h5>
              <p>
                Detailed information about various destinations including
                attractions, activities, accommodations, dining options,
                transportation, weather, and local customs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
            <div class="card">
              <img
                src="icons/enquiry.png"
                alt=""
                height="28%"
                width="28%"
                style="margin: 4vw 0 3vw 6vw"
              />
              <h5>Instant Enquiry</h5>
              <p>
                Experience seamless booking with our 'Instant Inquiry' feature.
                Simply click the WhatsApp icon to connect directly with our team
                and submit your inquiry instantly.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
            <div class="card">
              <img
                src="icons/reviews.png"
                alt=""
                height="28%"
                width="28%"
                style="margin: 4vw 0 3vw 6vw"
              />
              <h5>User Reviews and Ratings</h5>
              <p>
                User-generated reviews and ratings for hotels, restaurants,
                attractions, and other travel services to help users make
                informed decisions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="travel-blog">
      <h1 class="mb-4">Travel Blogs</h1>
      <h6 class="text-success text-center mb-4">Read About our Blogs</h6>
      <div class="row mx-4">
        <% TravelBlogs.forEach(travelBlog => { %>
        <div class="col col-lg-4 col-md-6 col-sm-12">
          <a href="/TravelBlog/<%= travelBlog._id %>">
            <div class="card border border-top-0">
              <div class="card-img-top mb-4">
                <img
                  src="<%= travelBlog.travelBlogImage %>"
                  alt="blog-img1"
                  height="60%"
                  width="100%"
                />
              </div>
              <h4 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-body-secondary pb-3 ps-3 pe-3">
                <%= travelBlog.travelBlogTitle %>
              </h4>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
        <% }) %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
